item.title: Add objects blanc source (defeult scape)
item.dc:creator: @ziplock ziplock
item.description:
@ziplock wrote:

Search for

    public void NewObjects() {

Under that add

makeGlobalObject(CORDX, CORDY, ID, DIRCTION, TYPE);

explains itself for direction and type here’s some help
DIRECTION:

0 = West || -1 = North || -2 = East || -3 = South

TYPE:

 0-3 wall objects, 4-8 wall decoration, 9: diag. walls, 10-11 world objects, 12-21: roofs, 22: floor decoration

Normally for normal object put the type as 10.
